title: SIX SIX SIXTH
body_text:
Season 17 Opener: DRAFT #6 Results
ECD's
roughest and toughest battle it out!
Team ONE Draft Selections
1. Jon Yochum -- 2. Caleb Flick -- 5. Ashley Hoppe -- 7. Ryan Letsche -- 9. Lenny Herrera -- 10. Kevin Fitzpatrick -- 13. Chris Adams
Team TWO Draft Selections
3. Travis Mills -- 4. John Tronolone -- 6. Mike "Sputz" Krott -- 8. Michael Edwards -- 11. Michelle Mullins -- 12. Kevin Megill -- 14. Eamon Fitzpatrick
Those involved in this 6th random selection of its kind were not the only ones who felt the unadulterated rage of their enemies. Team ONE, who went on to secure the hard-fought victory, acquired the likes of such superstars Jason Teilelbaum and former season finale veterans "Punter" Wolf and "The Piercer".
Though on the losing end of the event-long war, Team TWO also had its share of additional superstars; "The Big Kat" Zach Katz and kamikaze Steve Adams just to name two.
Flash Results by Game
ONE: 1, 2, 4, 5, 7
TWO: 3, 6
The Rules
: Classic two-team match-up.
The Match
: Team ONE defeated Team TWO, 5 - 2. Teams were formed via the
Dodgeball Draft
.
Moments & Stars
: hilarious Princess Peach-like dodges by Travis Mills; John Tronolone's explosive faceshot on Justin Pierce
Attendance
: 20, comprised of 17 men and 3 women
New Players
: Caleb Flick
Other Notes
: DODGEBALL 161 kicked off the 17th Season of
ECD
and hosted just the sixth
Dodgeball Draft
.
